---
const menuLinks = [
  { label: "Menus du Jour", href: "/menus/menus-de-la-semaine" },
  { label: "Menus du chef", href: "/menus/menus-du-chef" },
  { label: "Menus à la carte", href: "/menus/menus-a-la-carte" },
  { label: "Pizzas", href: "/menus/pizzas" },
  { label: "Burgers", href: "/menus/burgers" },
  { label: "Traiteur", href: "/menus/menus-traiteur" },
];
---

<footer class="border-t border-neutral-300 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-default">
    <!-- Footer Top: Logo -->
    <div class="border-b border-neutral-300 py-10 lg:py-20">
      <a href="/">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="La Croix des Landes" loading="lazy" class="max-w-[200px]" />
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Middle -->
    <div class="py-12 lg:py-30">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Left: Menus + Badge -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-10">
          <!-- Menu links -->
          <div>
            <div class="mb-10">
              <span class="text-200 uppercase tracking-wider font-medium text-neutral-800">Menus</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              {menuLinks.map(link => (
                <li>
                  <a href={link.href} class="text-100 uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-neutral-800 transition-colors">
                    {link.label}
                  </a>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Badge + Google Rating -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <span class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Excellent</span>
              <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/La+Croix+des+Landes" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
                ⭐ 4.7 / 5
              </a>
              <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500">basé sur 61 avis</span>
              <img src="/images/logo-badge.svg" alt="" class="h-5 mt-2" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Contact card -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-300 p-6 sm:p-10 lg:p-12">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-200 uppercase tracking-wider font-medium text-neutral-100">Nous joindre</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-2">
              <span class="text-200 font-medium text-neutral-100">Téléphone:</span>
              <a href="tel:0299719368" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-100 transition-colors tracking-wider uppercase">
                02 99 71 93 68
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-2">
              <span class="text-200 font-medium text-neutral-100">Email:</span>
              <span class="text-neutral-300 tracking-wider uppercase">lacroixdeslandes@orange.fr</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-neutral-600 my-8"></div>

          <div id="location-and-map" class="mb-6">
            <div class="mb-7">
              <span class="text-200 uppercase tracking-wider font-medium text-neutral-100">Localisation</span>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1 text-neutral-300">
              <div>Rue de La Croix des Landes</div>
              <div>56350 Saint Gorgon</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d64273.3338694949!2d-2.235075744129218!3d47.699470831436!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x480f91be20437bbb%3A0x2bea104ac4c8804!2sLa%20croix%20des%20landes!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1768918639934!5m2!1sfr!2sfr"
              width="100%"
              height="280"
              style="border:0; border-radius:12px;"
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            ></iframe>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-neutral-300">La Croix des Landes est un restaurant familial situé à Saint-Gorgon (Morbihan) entre Allaire et Malansac, à 15 min de Questembert et 20 min de Redon. Nous proposons une cuisine française traditionnelle, élaborée à partir de produits frais et locaux, avec des menus du jour variés chaque semaine, des burgers maison, des pizzas artisanales et des formules traiteur pour vos événements.</strong>
            <br /><br />
            <strong class="text-neutral-300">Notre équipe vous accueille du lundi au dimanche avec une ambiance chaleureuse.</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Bottom -->
    <div class="border-t border-neutral-300 py-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">
        Copyright 2024 © La Croix Des Landes - Fait par <a href="https://www.maxencenoel.fr" class="hover:text-neutral-800 transition-colors">maxencenoel.fr</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
